Welcome to Dungeon Eternal X
How can I help you?

There are a few things you should know about this server and how it differs from other servers.

Here is a list of some of the more important things you need to know before you get started in DeX.
There are 6, which one would you like to know about?
6: "Pure" Wizards, Sorcerers, and Druids recieve a bonus to the DC or other parts of their spells. See the Class Changes in the Library in Loftenwood Tavern

5: The spell true seeing gives the effects of see invisiblity and ultravision. If you have high enough listen or spot, then you will get the orginial effect of true seeing, which many players on this server call true true seeing (TTS).
4: Armors, weapons, helmets, and shields can be customized for free from your crafting skill menu.
3: Players are only allowed to gain experience with other players who are within a ten level range.
2: This is a PvP server. Player-killing (PK) is acceptable and is encouraged among players of any level.

1: There are no alignment restrictions on classes whatsoever. You can be an evil paladin, or a good palemaster, if you so choose. You are still required to meet all other prerequisites. This being said, alignment does play a big part in your time on the server. There are several factions on the server, and most are alignment based. They take pride in hunting those of other alignments.

It is a dangerous place, there are many monsters roaming freely in the lands, as well as some very powerful creatures.

Moreover this land is quite lawless. Loftenwood is protected by the guards but outside this city the some other adventurers are more fearsome than the monsters.

Be wary traveller.
Once you are ready to start adventuring, head either north to the Graveyard, or west to the Goblin lands.
This is Loftenwood, a rural city. Everything you need to start exploring these lands can be found here.
Is there anything else I should know?
What can you rell me about this land?
